<text id="02-output-contract" title="LLM Cost Optimization Plan Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the cost-plan artefact. Describes router / cache / batch / budget configuration per pipeline stage and expected savings band.</summary>

  <section title="JSON Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/llm-cost-plan.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["artefact_id", "pipeline", "stages", "global_budget", "version", "last_reviewed", "measurement_baseline_days"],
  "properties": {
    "artefact_id":  {"type": "string", "pattern": "^cop-[a-z0-9-]{6,}$"},
    "pipeline":     {"type": "string"},
    "measurement_baseline_days": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 7},
    "stages": {
      "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["stage", "current_cost_share", "actions"],
        "properties": {
          "stage":              {"type": "string"},
          "current_cost_share": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0, "maximum": 1},
          "output_token_share": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0, "maximum": 1},
          "actions": {
            "type": "array", "minItems": 1,
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["type", "rule_ref"],
              "properties": {
                "type":     {"enum": ["router", "prompt-cache", "response-cache", "batch", "prompt-redesign", "no-op"]},
                "rule_ref": {"type": "string"},
                "config":   {"type": "object"},
                "expected_savings_pct": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0, "maximum": 0.95}
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "global_budget": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["daily_soft_usd", "daily_hard_usd", "alert_at_pct"],
      "properties": {
        "daily_soft_usd": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0},
        "daily_hard_usd": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0},
        "alert_at_pct":   {"type": "number", "minimum": 0.5, "maximum": 1}
      }
    },
    "version":       {"type": "string", "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$"},
    "last_reviewed": {"type": "string", "format": "date"}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "artefact_id": "cop-rag-pipeline",
  "pipeline": "neromedia-news-rewrite",
  "measurement_baseline_days": 14,
  "stages": [
    {"stage": "classify", "current_cost_share": 0.30, "output_token_share": 0.10,
     "actions": [
       {"type": "router", "rule_ref": "route-by-complexity",
        "config": {"classifier_model": "claude-haiku-4-5"}, "expected_savings_pct": 0.65}
     ]},
    {"stage": "rewrite", "current_cost_share": 0.55, "output_token_share": 0.70,
     "actions": [
       {"type": "prompt-cache", "rule_ref": "cache-only-repeated-prefix",
        "config": {"prefix_tokens": 2400}, "expected_savings_pct": 0.40},
       {"type": "prompt-redesign", "rule_ref": "log-output-token-share",
        "config": {"target_output_pct": 0.45}, "expected_savings_pct": 0.20}
     ]},
    {"stage": "embed-archive", "current_cost_share": 0.15, "output_token_share": 0.05,
     "actions": [
       {"type": "batch", "rule_ref": "batch-the-offline",
        "config": {"batch_size": 1000}, "expected_savings_pct": 0.50}
     ]}
  ],
  "global_budget": {"daily_soft_usd": 25, "daily_hard_usd": 50, "alert_at_pct": 0.80},
  "version": "1.1.0",
  "last_reviewed": "2026-05-22"
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "artefact_id": "x",
  "pipeline": "rag",
  "measurement_baseline_days": 0,
  "stages": [{"stage": "all", "current_cost_share": 1.5, "actions": []}],
  "global_budget": {"daily_soft_usd": 100, "daily_hard_usd": 50, "alert_at_pct": 2}
}
]]></code>
    <note>artefact_id fails pattern; baseline 0 days violates measure-before-optimize rule; cost share &gt;1 impossible; stage has no actions; soft &gt; hard budget; alert_at_pct &gt; 1 (must be 0-1); missing version + last_reviewed.</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-cost-optimization.py">Validator that enforces this contract.</reference>

</text>
